Package: drcanalyser
Title: Analyse Cell-Viability / Dose-Response Assays
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Ben", "King", email = "bg.king@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reads Tecan SparkControl plate-reader exports, normalises intensities
    (IC/GI/GR), fits drc dose-response curves, and produces ggplot figures plus
    IC50/GI50/GR50 statistics.
